name: Rainbow Butterfly Unicorn Kitty
overview: When a spirited kitten acquires magical powers, it transforms her into a part rainbow, part butterfly and part unicorn hybrid, and she goes on adventures with her best friends, a book-smart owl and a yeti, across a magical world, called Mythlandia.

episodes.name: Purrfect Party
episodes.overview: Felicity worries that her powers won't measure up at a party for the most powerful and popular citizens in Mythlandia.

episodes.name: Anubis Newbie
episodes.overview: An ancient Anubis king tests Miguel to see if heâ€™s ready to leave Mythlandia and become the next ruler of the underworld.

episodes.name: Catlantic City
episodes.overview: When Felicity brings Miguel to Catlantic City, Miguel is locked up in the pound for being a dog.

episodes.name: Scaredy Cat
episodes.overview: Felicity, Miguel, Yana and Athena have to cross the frightening Phobia Forest in order to cash in their coupons for some free cupcakes.

episodes.name: Sleeping Yeti
episodes.overview: Yana eats a witch's apple and falls asleep, so Felicity and Miguel have to find a way to break the spell.

episodes.name: The Sand Crab Man
episodes.overview: Felicity is having so much fun at her party that she convinces the Sand Crab Man to take the night off, which causes chaos in Mythlandia.

episodes.name: The Loch Mess Monster
episodes.overview: Miguel is so messy that a creature named the Loch Mess Monster moves in with him.

episodes.name: Mighty Meow and Super Lucha
episodes.overview: Felicity and Miguel pretend to be real superheroes, drawing the wrath of a notorious supervillain named The Couch Potato.

episodes.name: The Green-Eyed Monster
episodes.overview: Miguel invites Chippy, a cute chipmunklike creature, to join him and Felicity on their friend-iversary, but Chippy isn't all she seems.

episodes.name: Nobody's Purrfect
episodes.overview: Felicity tries a little too hard to be purr-fect.

episodes.name: Gone with the Wand
episodes.overview: Felicity and friends find a magic wand, which they use to make crazy wishes until they can locate the wand's rightful owner.

episodes.name: Fountain of Too Much Youth
episodes.overview: Miguel discovers his favorite malt is now on the kids menu.

episodes.name: Snack Attack
episodes.overview: Felicity discovers her favorite snack has been sabotaged, so she takes matters into her own hands by visiting the Snacktory.

episodes.name: The Backward Bug
episodes.overview: The Backwards Bug bites Miguel and Athena, causing them to speak backward.

episodes.name: Mythic Mounties
episodes.overview: The friends join a scouting group, but Felicity has a hard time winning the praise of her scoutmaster and earning a merit badge.

episodes.name: Rainbow Butterfly Unicorn Cupid
episodes.overview: Moona announces she's closing Mythic Malts.

episodes.name: Denzel in Distress
episodes.overview: Felicity and Miguel rescue a prince named Denzel who's been imprisoned by his evil brother, Prince Larry.

episodes.name: Meanotaur
episodes.overview: When Felicity loses her favorite toy, she and her friends have to retrieve it from the yard of her dreaded neighbor, the Meanotaur.

episodes.name: The Boaracle
episodes.overview: The Boaracle, a boar who claims to predict the future, makes a series of predictions about Miguel that all come true.

episodes.name: Out of the Box
episodes.overview: When Felicity's fun unboxing videos go viral, a jealous Rudy slips Pandora's box into her scratching post house.

episodes.name: The Return of Mighty Meow and Super Lucha
The Trouble with Travis
episodes.overview: In order for a genie to grant more wishes, Felicity must get the last person who found the lamp to complete an unmade wish.

episodes.name: Tooth or Consequences
episodes.overview: Someone steals the gold coins the Saber Tooth Fairy exchanges for loose teeth.

episodes.name: The Boogie Man
episodes.overview: While getting ready for a big dance competition, Felicity starts having nightmares about the Boogie Man.

episodes.name: The Souper Monster
episodes.overview: In order to help Miguel win Mythlandia's annual cook-off competition, Felicity buys him a bag of magic beans.

episodes.name: The Winky
episodes.overview: Felicity is overwhelmed by the responsibility of owning her first pet, a cute but mischievous creature called a Winky.

episodes.name: Trivial Per Hoot
episodes.overview: Athena loses her confidence when, for the first time ever, she gets a fact about Mythlandia wrong.

episodes.name: Small Change
episodes.overview: Felicity questions what she's meant to be when she baby-sits a little changeling girl struggling with the same issue.

episodes.name: Rip Van Stinkle
episodes.overview: When Felicity comes to the aid of a stinky stranger named Rip Van Stinkle, he vows to be at her beck and call for life.

episodes.name: Excali-Burt
episodes.overview: Felicity pulls a legendary talking sword named "Excali-Burt" from a stone and is rewarded with her own magical castle.

episodes.name: Ratted Out
episodes.overview: Rudy begs Mighty Meow and Super Lucha to give him a shot at being their sidekick.
